Credits for Freevo
==================

$Id$



Packages/external code snippets:
--------------------------------

o mplayer: http://www.mplayerhq.hu
o NVrec: http://www.ee.up.ac.za/~justin/v4l2/
o XviD: http://www.xvid.org
o mp3_id.py: http://id3-py.sourceforge.net/
o jpgtn, used in part by osd_server: http://jpgtn.sourceforge.net/
o OSD image scaling, Dr Dobbs article in the April 1997 issue
  by Dean Clark, <71160.2426@compuserve.com>
o EXIF support from Thierry Bousch <bousch@topo.math.u-psud.fr>


